- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is another possible category as the paper deals with the complexity of a specific operation on DFAs.
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is a possible category as the paper deals with the algebraic expression of the state complexity, which is related to logical operations on DFAs.
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper uses some geometric intuition to explain the multiple catenation operation.
